posts.post_title: FS/FT - *EBAY BOUND* t206, t207, t210-2&3&6, t212-2&3 & more!
posts.post_content:
*Moving the unsold cards to eBay. All the T205's are on eBay. The rest of the unsold will be going up next week. If interested, let me know, thanks!

Finally getting around to listing all my dupes!
 
Will gladly talk trade. I collect most T cards, M101-2, C46, R316, N172 Denver players and pre-1930 boxing cards.
 
For buyers: I prefer PP F/F, you can send to [url]Jsrogoff71@gmail.com[/url]. Shipping is included for all cards! "I'll take it" will end any/all negotiations for that card. All cards are scanned with a high resolution scanner showing every blemish. With this in mind, I can guarantee they will all present better to the naked eye. Please feel free to ask me any questions concerning condition.
 
I do work a little different hours, so please be patient with my responses. I will respond in the order they are received. Thanks for looking!
 
All cards are viewable on Flickr, please click on the link.
[url]https://flic.kr/s/aHBqjA5L4C[/url]
